ext-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">; 刘起勇. IPCC AR6</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">报告解读：气候变化与人类健康[J]. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: 16px;\">气候变化研究进展</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">, 2022, 18(04):442-451.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">22. 钟爽; </span><b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">黄存瑞.</span></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> 气候变化的健康风险与卫生应对[J]. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px;\">科学通报</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">, 2019, 64(19):2002-2010.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">23.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><b style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">黄存瑞</span></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">; 王琼. 气候变化健康风险评估、早期信号捕捉及应对策略研究[J]. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: 16px;\">地球科学进展</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">, 2018, 33(11):1105-1111.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">24. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;\">韩阿珠; 邓诗舟; </span><b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;\">黄存瑞.</span></b> <span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;\">极端气温诱发哮喘发作的研究进展及其潜在影响机制探讨[J]. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-decoration: underline; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;\">中华预防医学杂志</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 150%; font-size: 16px;\">, 2022, 56(10):1452-1460.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">25. 王丽云; 王琼; </span><b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">黄存瑞.</span></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> 孕期高温暴露导致早产的机制研究进展[J]. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px;\">环境与职业医学</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">, 2022, 39(03):275-280.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">26.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><b style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">黄存瑞</span></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">; 邓诗舟. 气候变化下的新发传染病风险[J]. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: 16px;\">山东大学学报(医学版)</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">, &nbsp;2020, 58(10):7-12.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">27. 盛戎蓉; 高传思; 李畅畅; </span><b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">黄存瑞.</span></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> 全球气候变化对职业人群健康影响[J]. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px;\">中国公共卫生</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">, 2017, 33(08):1259-1263.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">28.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><b style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">黄存瑞</span></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">. 气候变化如何影响人类健康[J]. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: 16px;\">可持续发展经济导刊</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">, 2020, 5:26-28.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">29.</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><b style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">黄存瑞</span></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">. 极端天气事件频发，加剧人群健康风险[N]. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: 16px;\">健康报</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">, 2022-9-28.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 29px; text-indent: 0em; text-align: left; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">30.</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><b style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">黄存瑞</span></b><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">. 气候变化带来健康风险，我们如何应对[N]. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: 16px;\">光明日报</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: 0em; font-size: 16px;\">, 2022-8-27.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 150%; margin-top: 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">专著与教材</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 29px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">1. 《气候变化健康风险评估方法与应用》[M]. 北京：科学出版社, 2024.（主编）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 29px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">2. 《气候变化与健康100问》[M]. 北京：科学出版社, 2022.（主编）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 29px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">3. 《气候变化与人体健康》[M].北京：气象出版社, 2024.（副主编）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 29px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">4. 《公共卫生与健康》[M]. 北京：人民卫生出版社, 2024.（副主编）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 29px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">5. 《中国气候与生态环境演变：2021》[M]. 北京：科学出版社, 2022. （编委）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 29px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">6. 《气候变化绿皮书：碳达峰碳中和专辑》[M]. 北京：社会科学文献出版社, 2021.（编委）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 29px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">7. 《大流行：挑战与应对》[M]. 北京：科学技术文献出版社, 2023.（编委）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 29px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">8. 《全球健康研究方法》[M]. 北京：人民卫生出版社, 2018.（编委）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 29px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">9. </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 150%; fon